caller_intent: The caller attempted to reach Holly, a part-time agent, but was informed she was unavailable. They sought guidance on leaving a voicemail and confirmed her work schedule.
resolution_steps: Agent explained Holly's part-time schedule (9 AM–1 PM, Monday–Friday, with Friday off).
Offered to send the caller's message to Holly's voicemail.
Informed the caller Holly would see the voicemail the next day and contact them.
summary: The caller tried to reach Holly but was informed she was unavailable. The agent explained Holly's schedule, facilitated a voicemail, and assured the caller Holly would contact them the next day.
